This is an amazing collection of classical music for Christmas.  Very calming and soothing.  - Big Papi

A Classical Christmas 320cbr (Big Papi) 1990 Conducted by Erin Knight
-

By R.E. 
Over a dozen years ago, I purchased this same CD in London. It has been my favorite Christmas album ever since. However, the particular music is appropriate for any time of the year, and I certainly don't put it away after Christmas.
